    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will showcase signing in to the system, including:</p><ul><li><p>Log in/log out</p></li><li><p>Clock in/clock out</p></li><li><p>Assigning a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT)</p></li><li><p>Switching users</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/OjWZ-aThNPA\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/OjWZ-aThNPA</a><h2 id=\"LogIn/OutofRepairQ(video)-AdditionalResources\"> Additional Resources</h2><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1928921099/Getting+Started+Login+Password+Reset+and+User+Profile+Customization\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1928921099\" data-linked-resource-version=\"23\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Getting Started: Logging In/Out and Password Reset</a></p></li><li><p> <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1928986634/Getting+Started+Clock+In+Out+of+RepairQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1928986634\" data-linked-resource-version=\"23\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Clocking In/Out of RepairQ</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933901843/Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+Setup\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933901843\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Setting up a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT)</a></p></li></ul><p> </p>",
